      passage: `<p>Trustworthy machine learning is an approach that computer scientists like Meredith Ringel Morris use to engineer artificial intelligence technologies. It involves training computer algorithms to be accurate, safe, and fair. Unsupervised machine learning is another approach. ______ involves training computer algorithms to organize unlabeled data sets.</p>`,
